### Get All Users
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/users HTTP/1.1


### Get a Single User by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/users/5 HTTP/1.1


### Update a User by ID
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/auth/users/1 HTTP/1.1

Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Name",
  "email": "updatedemail@example.com"
}

### Delete a User by ID
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/auth/users/1 HTTP/1.1


### Sign Up a New User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/signup HTTP/1.1

Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "password": "securepassword",
  "fullName": "New User"
}

### Sign In an Existing User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/signin HTTP/1.1

Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "existinguser@example.com",
  "password": "securepassword"
}
